    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Artists who specialize in painting watercolors, which are works of art, generally on a paper support, to which pigment suspended in water is applied with a brush.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
